des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Fakro window or roller blind. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our Fakro Smart app in app market then register an account;
2. Configure our devices in our Fakro Smart app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
4. Find Fakro Smart skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
5. Enable Fakro Smart skill, and you'll be navigated to Fakro Smart login page;
6. Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
7. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, open your window to 50%"
"Alexa, close the window"
"Alexa, set the blinds to 20%"
"Alexa, open the blind"
